        <item>
            <title>Starlink 現金流實現收支平衡　將繼續發射更多衞星擴充網絡</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=starlink-breakeven-cash-flow</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 16:56:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SpaceX]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Starlink]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203046</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>SpaceX 的 Starlink 衞星網絡服務一直是他們的核心業務之一，近年密鑼緊鼓的擴充下，最近終於實現了現金流收支平衡，未來可望成為獨立公司上市招股。<br /><span id="more-1203046"></span></p><p>SpaceX 本身在 2022 年已經錄得現金流脫離赤字的軌道，而且在 2023 年也繼續錄得黑字，至於旗下 Starlink 衞星網絡服務，最近 Elon Musk 在 X 上透露也終於實現現金流收支平衡，同時已經佔有目前運作中衞星之中的最大份額，在明年內更會成為人類所發射的所有衞星之中，佔最大比例的種類。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Excited to announce that <a href="https://twitter.com/SpaceX?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@SpaceX</a><a href="https://twitter.com/Starlink?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Starlink</a> has achieved breakeven cash flow! Excellent work by a great team.</p><p>Starlink is also now a majority of all active satellites and will have launched a a majority of all satellites cumulatively from Earth by next year.</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1720098480037773658?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 2, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>目前為止 Starlink 已經發射超過 5,000 個衞星，用戶超過 200 萬，帶領 SpaceX 估值提升至超過 1,500 億美元。Elon Musk 之前曾經透露 Starlink 有機會分拆上市募資，不過就要等到最快 2025 年之後。</p><p>來源：X</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/">Starlink 現金流實現收支平衡　將繼續發射更多衞星擴充網絡</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
