        <item>
            <title>Samsung 推 Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro   靈感來自 2003 年 SGH-E700 手機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/galaxy-z-flip5-retro/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=galaxy-z-flip5-retro</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/galaxy-z-flip5-retro/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 04:24:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Z Flip5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SGH-E700]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202074</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 宣佈於 11 月 1 日率先於韓國、英國、德國、西班牙和澳洲推出 Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro，以紀念 2003 年推出的 SGH-E700，而法國版則於 11 月 2 日推出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202089" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip-5-Retro-Edition-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/641.jpeg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1202090" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/641.jpeg" alt="" width="540" height="304" /></a></p><p>Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro 的設計靈感來自 20 年前推出的 SGH-E700，再將其結合至 Galaxy Z Flip5 中，是款體現 Samsung 創新傳統的限量版手機。SGH-E700 在當年推出時以卓越的設計及性能俘獲市場，為 Samsung 首款內建天線的手機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main2.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main2-694x309.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="309" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main2-694x309.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main2-768x342.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main2.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro 繼承 SGH-E700 的各種獨特功能，如象徵式的靛藍色及銀色、重新詮釋 2000 年代像素圖形的用戶體驗設計，以及在 Flex Window 上描繪城市風景的獨家動畫，充滿懷舊氣息。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retrp_main3.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202077" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retrp_main3-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retrp_main3-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retrp_main3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retrp_main3.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro 更隨機附送三張印有 Samsung 不同時期標誌的 Flipsuit 卡片、Flipsuit 保護套，以及刻有獨特序號的收藏卡，增加 Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro 的收藏價值。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main4.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main4-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main4-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Galaxy-Z-Flip5-Retro_main4.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>除了 SGH-E700，Samsung 於數十年來推出一系列革命性的手機產品，當中包括 1999 年的 MP3 手機 SPH-M2500、手錶手機 SPH-WP10、電視手機 SCH-M220 及照相手機 SCH-V200，款款皆極具創意。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.samsung.com/global/samsung-electronics-unveils-galaxy-z-flip5-retro-to-celebrate-a-legacy-of-innovation">Samsung Newsroom</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/galaxy-z-flip5-retro/fun-tech/">Samsung 推 Galaxy Z Flip5 Retro   靈感來自 2003 年 SGH-E700 手機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
